Canfield

More than 100 solitaire variants if desired. 


RPG Progression

Earn gold from victories.

Buy new table themes.

Upgrade your home.

Unlock pets that provide bonuses.

Complete daily and weekly quests.

Level up your player.


Multiplayer

Leaderboards

Daily tournaments

Weekly championships

Friend challenges

Seasonal events


Graphics

Unreal Engine-quality visuals in Unity's Universal Render Pipeline (URP).

Animated cards.

Dynamic weather.

Day/night cycle.

Ambient wildlife and NPCs.

Console-quality lighting while remaining optimized for mobile.


For a premium mobile game, this approach creates something much larger than a standard solitaire app—it becomes an exploration game with solitaire at its core, giving players reasons to keep returning beyond simply completing hands.
